                        <img class="gallery-image " src="https://www.chowhound.com/img/gallery/the-little-known-history-behind-coca-cola-bottles/cokes-curves-1704827004.jpg" data-slide-url="https://www.chowhound.com/1489559/little-known-history-coca-cola-bottles/" data-post-id="1489559" data-slide-num="2" data-slide-title="The little known history behind Coca-Cola bottles: Coke's curves" width="780" height="438" alt="Coca-Cola bottling line">
